WEBVTT

00:05:59.720 --> 00:06:03.896
And governments do that
when they hand out subsidies

00:06:03.920 --> 00:06:07.480
to just the favorite few, the selected.

00:06:09.240 --> 00:06:12.296
They may do that
when they hand out subsidies --

00:06:12.320 --> 00:06:15.560
and, of course,
all financed by taxpayers --

00:06:16.680 --> 00:06:17.880
to companies.

00:06:18.760 --> 00:06:23.696
That may be in the form
of special tax treatments,

00:06:23.720 --> 00:06:25.136
like the tax benefits

00:06:25.160 --> 00:06:30.056
that firms like Fiat,
Starbucks and Apple got